title: New Eritrea
typeOfFood: Beer/Wine, Take-out, Eritrea, Ethiopian, African, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Eritrean and Ethiopian food. Has a menu list of vegan items, including tumtumo (lentil beans with spices, onions, herbs), hamu (collard greens and spinach in spices), veg allicha (seasoned mixture of potatoes, carrots, cabbage, garlic, ginger), and alicha-ater (chickpea in spices).
